	(text "per phase current sensor: LEM LZSR 80-P\n7.813 mV/A\n5V supply\nVout: 0.25 ~ 4.75 V\nVref: 2.485 ~ 2.515 V\n\ndiff gain = 1 => 15.626 mV/A\nOCP voltage set : 100A => 1.65+-0.7813 = 2.431,0.868\nOCP voltage actual: 2.431, 0.868"
		(exclude_from_sim no)
		(at 166.624 50.8 0)
